GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members

### 회원 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members/4

### 회원 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "no": 4,
  "name": "여우",
  "age": -1
}

### 500 - 예상하지 못한 서버 오류
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members/server-error